reviewText: As far as low budgets films go, this one gets my approval.  I've actually watched this one more than once, with different people and we make reference to scenes in the movie all the time....Ain't no mo, Ain't even no mo.................I'm going to bed, my head hurt!  Where she get dat gun?LOL, ROTF......I get it and that's all that matters!!Pancake alone will keep you laughin'.I recommend this to the easy going, black film supporters out there.

reviewText: If you want the truth... No one could have directd,casted,scripted this movie any better... Although the Gipp characters wardrobe could've looked more manish and less clownish, because his love interest Mia (Chrystal(eye candy) Wilson)shifted her character into all the right gears... Honestly this movie should've rated a "solid" 3***1/2 stars... The movies major flaw was its picture clarity & lighting quality (it sucked),... The cast gave 100% percent, The script was well written, Like I said another unbuffed buried jewell...
